metadata.name: starting at last
metadata.description:
Wang Xian whispered.



A year before reborn Datamation, he gambled everything.



Although we know that Bluestar will be digitized after a year, we are not completely sure, because who knows whether he is born again or has a mental problem.



But now, after all, he was right.



Open the Properties panel.



Wang Xian said in his heart.



"Please set a nickname first."
